{"title_page": "List of fictional vampires", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\n{{about||information on vampires|Vampire|a list of vampires or vampire-like legendary creatures of global folklore|List of vampires in folklore}}\n{{Expand list|date=June 2019}}\nThis is a '''list of fictional vampires''' found in [[literary fiction]], [[film]] and [[television]], [[comics]] and [[manga]], [[video games]] and [[board games]], and in [[musicals]], [[opera]] and [[theatre]]. It does not include vampires originating in folklore or mythology, or the concept of [[dhampir]]s, hybrid or half-vampires.\n\n{{TOC right}}\n\n==Literary==\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->\n\n<!--*****\nGuidelines:\n\nPlease post in alphabetical order! Once each list gets long enough, feel free to add sub-headings for each letter for easier navigation. Include ranges if not all letters are covered (i.e. X-Z). Unless a character's title is specifically part of their name (i.e. Count von Count of Sesame Street) or Count is used in the name of the character's corresponding Wiki article (i.e. Count Dracula), please refrain from listing the title when adding an entry, but rather place them alphabetically sans titles.\n\nThis article is a list, please do not break from the format when adding examples. Each entry's respective articles should provide any explanation if needed, as such there is no reason to post summaries. If you feel a need to justify your entry, include it in comments following your edit so you can alert future editors as to your reasoning without disrupting the flow of the article.\n\nMake sure to always include both the character and the work of fiction the character is from. If it is the case that the character appears in more than one category, make sure to link to the correct page. For example, D from Vampire Hunter D is currently in every category but each fiction link is to the telcorresponding version's (literary, film, manga, video game, etc.) correct wiki article. If separate articles for medium do not exist, link to the main series or character article.\n\nThanks.\n***** -->\n\n===A===\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->\n\n{{anchor|Literary A}}\n* Aaron Darnell (''[[Women of the Otherworld]]'')\n* Abby Bennett Wilson (''[[The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* Addh\u00e9ma ([[Paul F\u00e9val, p\u00e8re|F\u00e9val]]'s ''La Vampire'')\n* [[List of Vampire Academy characters#Adrian Ivashkov|Adrian Ivashkov]] (''[[Vampire Academy]]'')\n* [[The Vampire Chronicles|Akasha]] (''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'')\n* Alan Raby (''[[The Phantom (play)|The Phantom]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#The Volturi|Alec]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* Alexander Sterling (''[[Vampire Kisses]]'')\n* [[Akivasha]] (books and stories by [[Robert E. Howard]])\n* Alaric Saltzman (''[[The Vampire Diaries (novel series)|The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* [[Alice Cullen (Twilight)|Alice Cullen]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* Alistair (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* Amara (''[[The Vampire Diaries (novel series)|The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* [[The Morganville Vampires#Characters|Amelie]] (''[[The Morganville Vampires]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#Egyptian coven|Amun]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* Annabelle (''[[The Vampire Diaries (novel series)|The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* [[List of The Southern Vampire Mysteries characters#Andre Paul|Andre Paul]] (''[[The Southern Vampire Mysteries]]'')\n* [[Angel (Buffy the Vampire Slayer)|Angel]] (''[[Buffy novels|Buffy the Vampire Slayer]]'', ''[[Angel novels|Angel]]'')\n* [[Anita Blake]] (''[[Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter]]'')\n* [[Der kleine Vampir|Anna von Schlotterstein]] (''[[Der kleine Vampir|The Little Vampire]]'')\n* Anthea Ernchester (''[[Those Who Hunt the Night]]'', ''[[Traveling with the Dead]]'')\n* Aoife (''[[The Necromancer: The Secrets of the Immortal Nicholas Flamel]]'')\n* [[Armand (The Vampire Chronicles)|Armand]] (''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#The Volturi|Aro]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* [[List of The Saga of Darren Shan characters#Arra Sails|Arra Sails]] (''[[The Saga of Darren Shan]]'')\n* [[List of The Saga of Darren Shan characters#Arrow|Arrow]] (''[[The Saga of Darren Shan]]'')\n* [[Night World#Main vampire characters|Ash Redfern]] (''[[Night World]]'')\n* [[Asher (Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter)|Asher]] (''[[Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#The Volturi|Athenodora]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* [[In the Forests of the Night#Character list|Ather]] (''[[In the Forests of the Night]]'')\n* [[In the Forests of the Night#Character list|Aubrey]] (''[[In the Forests of the Night]]'')\n* [[List of Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter characters#Aubrey|Aubrey]] (''[[Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter]]'')\n* [[List of Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter characters#Augustine|Augustine]] (''[[Anita Blake: Vampire Hunter]]'')\n* [[Avicus (The Vampire Chronicles)|Avicus]] (''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'' )\n* Azusa Mukami (''[[Diabolik Lovers]]'')\n\n===B===\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->{{anchor|Literary B}}\n* [[List of Evernight characters#Balthazar More|Balthazar More]] (''[[Evernight (series)|Evernight]]'')\n* [[Barnabas Collins]] (''[[Dark Shadows#Novels|Dark Shadows]]'' novels)\n* [[Bella Cullen]] (''[[Breaking Dawn]]''){{efn|name=\"later\"}} \n* Ben Cortman (''[[I Am Legend (novel)|I Am Legend]]'')\n* Ben McKittrick (''[[The Vampire Diaries (novel series)|The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#Egyptian coven|Benjamin]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* [[Blue Bloods (novel series)#The Force family|Benjamin \"Jack\" Force]] (''[[Blue Bloods (novel series)|Blue Bloods]]'')\n* [[List of The Vampire Chronicles characters#Main|Bianca Solderini]] (''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'')\n* [[List of The Dr