fan]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* [[Stefan Salvatore]] (''[[The Vampire Diaries (novel series)|The Vampire Diaries]]'')\n* [[Tempted (Cast novel)|Stevie Rae Johnson]] (''[[House of Night]]'' series)\n* Mrs. Stone (''[[The Room in the Tower]]'')\n* [[Strahd von Zarovich]] ([[Ravenloft#Novels|''Ravenloft'' novels]])\n* Straits/Straizo (''[[JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Phantom Blood]]'')\n* [[List of Twilight characters#The Volturi|Sulpicia]] ([[Twilight (novel series)|''Twilight'']] series)\n\n===T===\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->{{anchor|Literary T}}\n* [[List of Twilight characters#Denali coven|Tanya]] (''[[Twilight (novel series)|Twilight]]'' series)\n* [[List of Vampire Academy characters#Queen Tatiana Ivashkov|Tatiana Ivashkov]] (''[[Vampire Academy]]'')\n* [[List of The Vampire Chronicles characters#Main|Tarquin \"Quinn\" Blackwood]] (''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'')\n* Theodore \"Fat Teddy\" Bottari (''The Blood Maker and the Witch's Curse'')\n* [[Night World#Soulmate|Thierry Descoudres]] (''[[Night World]]'')\n* [[Necroscope (novel)|Thibor Ferenczy]] (''[[Necroscope]]'' series)\n* [[Thomas Raith]] (''[[The Dresden Files]]'')\n* [[Night World#The Chosen|Timmy Jordan]] (''[[Night World]]'')\n* [[Eleventh Grade Burns#Main characters|Tomas Tod]] (''[[The Chronicles of Vladimir Tod]]'')\n* Thuringwethil (''[[The Silmarillion]]'')\n* [[Lost Souls (Poppy Z. Brite novel)#Twig and Molochai|Twig]] (''[[Lost Souls (Poppy Z. Brite novel)|Lost Souls]]'')\n* [[Carry On (novel)#Main characters|Tyrannus Basilton \"Baz\" Grimm-Pitch]] (''[[Carry On (novel)|Carry On]]'')\n\n===U===\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->{{anchor|Literary U}}\n\n===V===\n<!--*****JUST FOR CHARACTERS FOUND IN BOOKS*****-->{{anchor|Literary V}}\n* Valentine Cutter (''[[Shadow Zone (novels)|Shadow Zone: The Undead Express]]'')\n* [[Blood Brothers (Lumley novel)|Vasagi the Suck]] ([[Necroscope|''The Necroscope'' series]])\n* [[List of Vampire 