t when adding examples. Each entry's respective articles should provide any explanation if needed, as such there is no reason to post summaries. If you feel a need to justify your entry, include it in comments following your edit so you can alert future editors as to your reasoning without disrupting the flow of the article.\n\nMake sure to always include both the character and the work of fiction the character is from. If it is the case that the character appears in more than one category, make sure to link to the correct page. For example, D from Vampire Hunter D is currently in every category but each fiction link is to the corresponding version's (literary, film, manga, video game, etc.) correct wiki article. If separate articles for medium do not exist, link to the main series or character article.\n\nThanks.\n***** -->\n\n\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Role\n! Title\n! Notes\n! Refs\n|-\n| [[List of Let the Right One In characters#Eli or Abby|Abby]] || ''[[Let Me In (film)|Let Me In]]'' || || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/chloe-moretz-interview-let-me-in-hugo-cabret-emily-the-strange/ |title=Chloe Moretz Exclusive Interview LET ME IN; Plus Updates on EMILY THE STRANGE, HUGO CABRET, HICK and THE RUT |author=Christina Radish  |accessdate=16 October 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[List of The Vampire Diaries characters#Bonnie Bennett|Abby Bennett Wilson]] || ''[[The Vampire Diaries]]'' || ||<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/gossip/la-et-mg-joseph-morgan-engaged-persia-white-the-originals-20140515-story.html |title='Originals' star Joseph Morgan engaged to 'Vampire Diaries' costar |author=Christina Radish |accessdate=16 October 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Abel Nightroad]] || ''[[Trinity Blood#Anime|Trinity Blood]]'' || ||\n|-\n|Abhay Raichand || ''[[Pyaar Kii Ye Ek Kahaani]]'' || ||<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/vivian-dsena-wants-to-play-a-vampire-again/story-OfHXy774Rj2zRZR3q0gCOM.html |title=Vivian Dsena want