ulture/306674-zvezda-seryala-splyt-krystyna-brodskaia-nash-proekt-sravnyvauit-s-potteryanoi |title=\u0417\u0432\u0435\u0437\u0434\u0430 \u0441\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0430\u043b\u0430 \"\u0421\u043f\u043b\u0438\u0442\" \u041a\u0440\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u0411\u0420\u041e\u0414\u0421\u041a\u0410\u042f: \"\u041d\u0430\u0448 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0435\u043a\u0442 \u0441\u0440\u0430\u0432\u043d\u0438\u0432\u0430\u044e\u0442 \u0441 \"\u043f\u043e\u0442\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0439\" - KP.UA|accessdate =6 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Leopold 'Leo' Zachs || ''[[Split (TV series)|Split]]'' || ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.funticles.com/electric-sheep/ |title=Electric Sheep begins online broadcast of Split's second season in South America|accessdate =6 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hot.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3882532,00.html|title=Ynet \u05dc\u05d9\u05d0\u05d5 - \u05d9\u05d5\u05df \u05ea\u05d5\u05de\u05e8\u05e7\u05d9\u05df - HOT.|accessdate=6 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Lestat de Lioncourt]] || ''[[Interview with the Vampire (film)|Interview with the Vampire]]'', ''[[Queen of the Damned]]'' || ||\n|-\n| [[List of The Vampire Diaries characters#Lexi Branson|Lexi Branson]] || ''[[The Vampire Diaries]]'' || ||\n|-\n| Lighthammer || ''[[Blade II]]'' || ||\n|-\n| Lillie Langtry || ''[[Kindred: The Embraced]]'' || ||<ref name=KTEM/>\n|-\n| [[Lily Munster]] || ''[[The Munsters]]'' || ||\n|-\n| Lionel \"Elvis\" Cormac || ''[[Daybreakers]]'' || ||\n|-\n| [[List of The Vampire Diaries characters#Season one|Logan Fell]] || ''[[The Vampire Diaries]]'' || ||\n|-\n| [[Lorena Krasiki]] || ''[[True Blood]]'' || ||\n|-\n| Lucien LaCroix || ''[[Forever Knight]]'' || ||\n|-\n| Lucifer || ''[[Dragon Ball: Sleeping Princess in Devil's Castle]]'' || ||\n|-\n| [[List of minor Buffy the Vampire Slayer characters#Luke|Luke]] || ''[[Buffy the Vampire Slayer (TV series)|Buffy the Vampire Slayer]]'' || ||<ref name=C&L/>\n|-\n| [[Millennium (Hellsi