va|Diva]] (''[[Blood+]]'')\n* Dolorosa (The Dolorosa) (''[[Homestuck]]'')\n* [[List of Tsukuyomi: Moon Phase characters|Elfriede]] (''[[Tsukuyomi: Moon Phase]]'')\n* [[Evangeline A.K. McDowell]] (''[[Negima]]'' and ''[[UQ Holder!]]'' series)\n* [[Fai D. Flowright]] (''[[Tsubasa: Reservoir Chronicle]]''){{efn|name=\"later\"|This character becomes a vampire later in the series.}}\n* [[List of Seraph of the End characters#Ferid Bathory|Ferid Bathory]] (''[[Seraph of the End]]'')\n* [[List of Chibi Vampire characters#Glark|Glark]] (''[[Chibi Vampire]]'')\n* Guilt-na-Zan (''[[Vampire Doll: Guilt-Na-Zan]]'')\n* [[List of Blood+ characters#Hagi.2FHaji|Haji]] (''[[Blood+]]'')\n* [[List of Vampire Knight characters#Hanabusa Aido|Hanabusa Aido]] (''[[Vampire Knight]]'')\n* [[Harmony Kendall|Harmony]] (''[[Buffy the Vampire Slayer comics|Buffy comics]]''/''[[Buffyverse comics]]''/''[[Angel comics]]'')\n* Hazuki/Luna (''[[Tsukuyomi: Moon Phase]]'')\n* [[List of Chibi Vampire characters#Henry Marker|Henry Marker]] (''[[Chibi Vampire]]'')\n* [[List of Rosario + Vampire characters#Issa Shuzen|Issa Shuzen]] (''[[Rosario+Vampire]]'')\n* Jeremiah Parrish (''[[Astro City]]'')\n* Jiro Mochizuki (''[[Black Blood Brothers]]'')\n* [[Jules Duchon]] (''[[Andrew Fox (author)|Fat White Vampire Blues]]'')\n* [[List of Rosario + Vampire characters#Kahlua Shuzen|Kahlua Shuzen]] (''[[Rosario+Vampire]]'')\n* [[Kamui Shir\u014d]] (''[[Tsubasa: Reservoir Chronicle]]'')\n* [[List of Vampire Knight characters#Kaname Kuran|Kaname Kuran]] (''[[Vampire Knight]]'')\n* Kanaya Maryam (''[[Homestuck]]'')\n* [[List of Chibi Vampire characters#Karin Maaka|Karin Maaka]] (''[[Chibi Vampire]]'' light novels)\n* [[List of Monogatari characters|Kiss-shot Acerola-orion Heart-under-blade]] (''[[Bakemonogatari]]'')\n* [[List of Rosario + Vampire characters#Koko Shuzen|Koko Shuzen]] (''[[Rosario+Vampire]]'')\n* Kojou Akatsuki (''[[Strike the Blood]]'')\n* Koyomi Araragi (''[[Monogatari Series]]'')\n* [[List of Seraph o